'''NAVCOR Command''' was an command unit of the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]]. [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Kemel Trowe]] was assigned to the command when they released a statement indicating that [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] was destroyed due to [[Bail Prestor Organa/Legends|Bail Prestor Organa]] initiating a biowar project in association with the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]].

